title: Act3_Judge_N0
---
/// no repeat
<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: Killed by a human this time? That’s new.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Is this just entertainment to you?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: I work all day long! Don’t blame me for finding joy in the little things.
The Judge: Who knows how long I’ll have to watch you run in circles before you kill the other false human.  

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Why did that woman think it was me?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Judge>>
The Judge: Just keep your head down and focus on saving Prism. Meeting adjourned!

<<player_respawn YarnManager>>
===


