title: Act3_PreCombat_Boss
---
/// no repeat
<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: Cyrus?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: …

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: Is something wrong?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Eve, all this time we’ve spent in the outskirts, and I’ve never seen the monsters attack you.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: …What?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Be honest with me. Are you a false human?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: I-I didn’t…Why would you think that?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Eve-

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: That’s not proof. That’s just... you guessing.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: I’m not trying to-

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: I’m your dispatcher. I’ve been helping you. I’ve been trying to keep people safe.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Eve, I know what happened to your sister.

Eve, overwhelmed, turns to the wall. (TODO)

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: …
Eve: She…you don’t understand.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Then help me understand.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: Cyrus, what does justice mean to you? 

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: It means protecting the good in this world.

Eve turns around with glowing eyes and a serene smile, showing she’s been possessed by the Hierophant. (TODO)

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: Then why are you working against it?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Urgh! You-!

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: After the Assimilation, there will be no more discord or pain. Eve was created to bring this peace.
Eve: Under the Hierophant, we will all be one.
===